('Hanging aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/laiLxov.jpg', 1.99, 'A space-saving design that hangs from the ceiling or a frame, ideal for small spaces.','The Hanging Aquarium is an innovative and space-saving design that offers a unique way to display aquatic life. Ideal for homes, offices, or any small spaces, this aquarium is designed to be suspended from the ceiling or mounted on a frame, allowing it to float effortlessly in mid-air. Its minimalist and contemporary aesthetic makes it a perfect choice for those looking for a stylish and functional piece of décor. Unlike traditional aquariums that sit on the floor or a shelf, the hanging design frees up valuable space, making it suitable for apartments, workspaces, or areas with limited room. The aquarium’s design is simple yet elegant, ensuring it complements various interior styles, from modern to industrial. The transparent glass material provides an unobstructed view of the aquatic environment inside, offering a serene and peaceful atmosphere. Whether it’s used to house small fish, aquatic plants, or decorative elements, the hanging aquarium becomes a focal point of any room. The compact size and hanging feature also make it easy to move and reposition, offering flexibility in how it’s displayed. Despite its small size, the aquarium provides ample space for fish to swim comfortably, making it a perfect home for Betta fish, shrimp, or other small aquatic creatures. Additionally, the hanging aquarium can be a conversation starter and a novelty piece that adds a touch of nature to your living or working environment. Its ability to save space while providing a calming and beautiful display of aquatic life makes it a great option for anyone who wants to enjoy the benefits of owning an aquarium without taking up too much space. This aquarium is easy to maintain, requiring minimal effort to keep the water clean and clear. Its unique design and functionality make it a standout piece, providing an extraordinary way to bring nature into your home or workspace. Whether it’s for the aesthetic appeal or the calming effect it brings, the Hanging Aquarium is an excellent choice for those who appreciate innovation and style in their décor', 80, 'Mountable'),
('Round aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/axL4qTN.jpg', 58.70, 'A spherical shape, providing an aesthetic and balanced display for small fish.','The Round Aquarium is a uniquely designed, spherical-shaped aquarium that offers an aesthetically pleasing and balanced display for small fish and aquatic plants. Its rounded structure not only creates a beautiful, uninterrupted view but also ensures that your fish are visible from all angles, making it a perfect addition to any home or office. This aquarium stands out due to its compact size and modern design, ideal for those who appreciate elegance and simplicity in their décor. The smooth, curved glass provides a panoramic view of the aquatic environment, allowing the fish to swim freely in a spacious, visually captivating setting. Whether you choose to place it on a desk, a coffee table, or a shelf, the Round Aquarium will undoubtedly become a focal point in any room, attracting attention and admiration from anyone who enters. Its spherical shape creates a harmonious blend of form and function, offering an even distribution of space inside for your aquatic life. The design is not only visually appealing but also practical, as it allows for easy viewing of your fish from various angles without the need for complex setup or maintenance. Additionally, the Round Aquarium is designed to accommodate a variety of small fish species, making it a versatile option for both beginners and seasoned aquarium enthusiasts. The ample space inside allows for the inclusion of decorative elements like plants, pebbles, or aquatic accessories, helping to create a vibrant and lively underwater world. Its small footprint ensures that it can fit seamlessly into any room, making it a great choice for individuals living in apartments or smaller spaces. Whether you Are looking to add a serene touch to your living room or a relaxing focal point to your office, the Round Aquarium is the perfect solution. Its minimalistic design coupled with the elegan