('Oval Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/KSQj96t.jpg', 90.24, 'An oval-shaped design providing more surface area for aquatic life and plants.','The Oval Aquarium is a unique and elegant addition to any space, offering an innovative design that combines functionality with aesthetic appeal. With its smooth, oval shape, it provides an expansive surface area, creating an optimal environment for aquatic life. This shape allows for better water circulation, which is crucial for the health of fish and plants within the aquarium. It is designed to be both practical and visually striking, making it perfect for homes, offices, or any space where you want to add a touch of nature. The increased surface area enhances the oxygen exchange in the water, creating a healthier environment for the fish and plants. The aquarium’s design not only ensures a more spacious habitat but also promotes a beautiful view of aquatic life from multiple angles. Whether you’re a novice aquarium enthusiast or a seasoned aquarist, the Oval Aquarium offers the flexibility to create a wide range of aquatic ecosystems. From freshwater setups to more complex saltwater environments, this aquarium is well-suited for various types of fish and plants. The oval shape also allows for greater creativity in terms of aquascaping, allowing you to arrange rocks, plants, and other decorative elements in a way that suits your personal taste. Additionally, its size and shape make it ideal for species that require more space to swim and grow, such as larger fish or certain plant species that need ample room for root expansion. This aquarium serves as not only a practical habitat for aquatic life but also a stunning centerpiece that brings nature indoors. It can be placed in any room where you wish to create a calming and tranquil atmosphere. The clarity of the glass ensures a pristine view of your aquatic environment, and the oval shape creates a sense of movement, as the fish appear to glide effortlessly through the water. The Oval Aquarium is built with durability in mind, constructed from high-quality materials that provide a sturdy and long-lasting enclosure. Whether you are looking to enhance the ambiance of your living room, office, or any other space, the Oval Aquarium is sure to be a conversation starter and a beautiful addition to your decor. Its sleek and modern design makes it a versatile piece that complements a variety of interior styles, from contemporary to traditional. The Oval Aquarium is more than just a tank; it’s a statement piece that brings life and serenity into any room', 140, 'Shaped'),
('Flowerhorn Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/THRgfYA.jpg', 98.32, 'Designed specifically for Flowerhorn fish, providing ample space for growth and display.','The Flowerhorn Aquarium is specifically designed to provide the ideal environment for Flowerhorn cichlids, one of the most unique and popular fish species in the aquarium hobby. Known for their vibrant colors and distinctive "kok" or head hump, Flowerhorn fish require a spacious and well-maintained aquarium to thrive. This aquarium features a large, open space that allows Flowerhorns to move freely and display their full beauty, which is essential for their health and development. The tank is built to accommodate the large size of these fish, providing ample swimming space while offering an aesthetically pleasing view of the fish from every angle. The design of the aquarium is not only functional but also visually striking, with its clean lines and sleek construction. The aquarium"s shape ensures that Flowerhorns can swim in all directions, mimicking their natural habitat where they enjoy a wide range of movement. It is equipped with advanced filtration systems to maintain clean, clear water, which is crucial for Flowerhorns, as they are sensitive to water quality changes. Regular water changes and a balanced filtration system help in preventing the buildup of toxins and waste, ensuring the well-being of the fish. In addition to its practical features, the Flowerhorn Aquarium is also an eye-catching decorative piece that can enhance the decor of any room. The aquarium"s elegant design complements the vivid colors and unique features of the Flowerhorn cichlid, making it a focal point in any living space. Whether placed in a living room, office, or other areas, it creates a visually striking display that draws attention and admiration. The aquarium"s size and design make it suitable for both beginners and experienced aquarium enthusiasts. With proper care and attention to water quality, lighting, and feeding, the Flowerhorn Aquarium provides the perfect home for these fascinating fish, allowing them to flourish and become a stunning centerpiece of any aquarium collection.', 2, 'Specialized'),
('Aquascape Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/3Vk7UyK.png', 133.45, 'Built to create a natural aquatic environment with plants, rocks, and aquatic life.','The Aquascape Aquarium is designed to recreate a natural aquatic environment, offering a harmonious blend of plants, rocks, and aquatic life to create a breathtaking aquatic ecosystem. Its design focuses on providing an optimal space for fish to thrive while also ensuring that plants and other elements can grow and flourish. The tank’s layout allows for an immersive underwater landscape that simulates a river, lake, or even the ocean, depending on the style chosen. The glass construction ensures clarity and visibility, allowing you to admire the intricate details of the aquascape. The aquarium"s spacious interior gives you the freedom to experiment with various aquascaping techniques, such as the Dutch style, Iwagumi, or Nature Aquarium, all of which create stunning visual effects and a sense of balance. With a high-quality filtration system, the Aquascape Aquarium maintains a healthy and clean environment for your fish and plants. The carefully designed filtration ensures that the water remains clear, removing impurities and maintaining optimal water conditions for both the aquatic plants and the fish. Additionally, the aquarium comes with adjustable lighting that mimics natural daylight, enhancing plant growth and highlighting the beauty of the underwater world. The aquatic plants, ranging from easy-to-care-for species to more delicate varieties, thrive in the controlled environment created by the Aquascape Aquarium. The rocks and decorations, carefully selected and arranged, form beautiful focal points that draw the eye and create a sense of depth and dimension within the aquarium. As the plants grow and the fish swim gracefully through the aquascape, the aquarium becomes a living piece of art, constantly evolving. Whether you are an experienced aquascaper or a beginner, the Aquascape Aquarium provides the perfect foundation for creating a beautiful and serene underwater world. Its combination of aesthetic appeal and practical functionality makes it a must-have for any aquarium enthusiast, offering a peaceful and relaxing atmosphere in any home or office. By investing in an Aquascape Aquarium, you are not just purchasing a tank; you are creating a dynamic aquatic ecosystem that provides both beauty and a sense of tranquility.', 130, 'Specialized'),
('Arowana Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/zSHnZdd.jpg', 264.57, 'Large and spacious, designed to accommodate the Arowana fish with plenty of swimming space.','The Arowana Aquarium is a premium, large-scale aquarium designed specifically to cater to the needs of the majestic Arowana fish, known for its grace and elegance. This aquarium is crafted to provide a spacious and visually stunning environment that allows the Arowana to swim freely and comfortably, mimicking the expansive natural habitats that these fish thrive in. With a substantial size and ample space, it ensures that the Arowana, which can grow to impressive lengths, has enough room to move, explore, and exhibit its natural behavior. The Arowana Aquarium features clear, high-quality glass panels that offer an unobstructed 360-degree view, allowing for optimal viewing from all angles, ensuring that the aquarium becomes a beautiful centerpiece in any room or space. The design of the aquarium emphasizes functionality and aesthetics, with a sleek and modern structure that complements various home or office decor styles. The large water volume of the aquarium ensures stability in water parameters, such as temperature and pH levels, which are crucial for the health and well-being of the Arowana fish. This feature makes it easier for owners to maintain optimal water conditions, contributing to a healthier environment for their fish. The aquarium’s filtration system is built to handle the high demands of keeping large fish like the Arowana, ensuring that the water remains clear, clean, and free of harmful toxins. The aquarium’s spaciousness is not only ideal for the Arowana but also allows for the introduction of other compatible fish or aquatic plants, enabling aquascaping enthusiasts to create a dynamic and vibrant underwater ecosystem. Overall, the Arowana Aquarium offers a perfect balance of size, functionality, and aesthetic appeal, making it the ideal choice for those looking to provide their Arowana with the perfect habitat while adding an elegant touch to their living or office space.', 110, 'Specialized'),
