('Bonded Glass Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/4rMjMn5.jpg', 347.25, 'Assembled with multiple glass panels bonded together, offering a sturdy and leak-proof design.','The Bonded Glass Aquarium is a beautifully crafted aquarium designed for those who appreciate both form and function in their aquatic displays. This aquarium is constructed using multiple glass panels that are meticulously bonded together to create a sturdy, leak-proof structure. The seamless connection of these panels ensures durability and strength, providing a reliable environment for your fish and aquatic plants. With its crystal-clear glass, the Bonded Glass Aquarium offers an unobstructed view of the aquatic world inside, allowing you to enjoy the graceful movement of fish and the beauty of underwater plants from every angle. Its elegant and minimalist design makes it a perfect fit for any modern home or office decor. Whether placed on a table, countertop, or stand, the aquarium serves as a captivating centerpiece that draws attention and admiration. The glass panels are polished to a smooth finish, adding to the overall sleekness and refinement of the aquarium. This type of aquarium is perfect for those who want a more sophisticated and refined look for their aquatic setup while maintaining a functional and easy-to-maintain design. The Bonded Glass Aquarium also provides ample space for fish to swim and plants to grow, ensuring a healthy and vibrant aquatic ecosystem. With proper filtration and lighting, this aquarium will be a perfect home for a variety of fish species, from small tropical fish to larger ornamental species. Additionally, the aquarium is strong and secure construction minimizes the risk of cracks or leaks, ensuring long-term reliability and peace of mind. The Bonded Glass Aquarium is not just a functional piece for housing aquatic life; it is also a work of art that enhances the aesthetic appeal of any space. The transparency of the glass, combined with its clean and modern lines, creates an inviting atmosphere, making it a focal point of the room. It is suitable for both experienced aquarium enthusiasts and beginners who want to add a touch of elegance and sophistication to their aquatic hobby. Whether you are starting a new aquarium setup or upgrading your current one, the Bonded Glass Aquarium offers the perfect combination of beauty, practicality, and durability, making it an ideal choice for anyone seeking to create a stunning aquatic display', 140, 'Glass'),
('Glass Cup Aquarium', 'https://i.imgur.com/BnZGuuL.jpg', 675.43, 'A small aquarium shaped like a cup, perfect for small fish or as a stylish decorative piece.','The Glass Cup Aquarium is a unique and stylish aquarium designed for those who appreciate minimalist aesthetics combined with functionality. This small, delicate aquarium takes the shape of a traditional cup, offering a compact yet striking way to house small fish or aquatic plants. The transparent glass construction allows for a clear, unobstructed view of its contents, providing a serene and visually appealing display. Its petite size makes it ideal for limited spaces such as desks, bedside tables, or even as a decorative piece on shelves, blending effortlessly into any room is decor. The Glass Cup Aquarium is perfect for those who enjoy keeping small fish species like Betta fish, guppies, or shrimp, as its compact size offers just enough room for these small creatures to thrive. Despite its size, the aquarium does not compromise on quality, as the glass is thick and sturdy, ensuring durability and long-term use. The minimalistic design of the aquarium also allows for creative and personalized decorations, allowing the owner to incorporate plants, stones, or decorative accessories to create a miniature aquatic world. Its simplicity makes it an excellent choice for beginners or anyone seeking a low-maintenance aquarium. The Glass Cup Aquarium also offers a calming, meditative quality, as the gentle movements of the fish and the tranquil water create a peaceful ambiance, perfect for relaxation and stress relief. Additionally, its design encourages responsible aquarism by fostering a space where owners can learn about the needs of aquatic life and the balance required to maintain a healthy, thriving ecosystem. Whether as a gift or as a functional piece of decor, the Glass Cup Aquarium offers both beauty and practicality, enhancing any space with its modern and elegant design.', 190, 'Glass'),
